{"id":"api/forms/RequiredValidator","title":"RequiredValidator","contents":"\n\n<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/forms\", \"name\": \"@angular/forms\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/forms/RequiredValidator\", \"name\": \"RequiredValidator\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/forms\">@angular/forms</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/forms/src/directives/validators.ts?message=docs(forms)%3A%20请简述你的修改...#L349-L425\" aria-label=\"提供编辑建议\" title=\"提供编辑建议\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/12.1.0-next.1/packages/forms/src/directives/validators.ts#L349-L425\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  \n  <header ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"requiredvalidator\">RequiredValidator<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/RequiredValidator#requiredvalidator\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    \n    <label class=\"api-type-label directive\">directive</label>\n    \n    \n    \n  </header>\n  \n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n    \n  <section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"short-description\">\n    <p translation-result=\"on\">该指令会借助 <code><a href=\"api/forms/NG_VALIDATORS\" class=\"code-anchor\">NG_VALIDATORS</a></code> 绑定把 <code>required</code> 验证器添加到任何带 <code>required</code> 属性的控件上。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">A directive that adds the <code>required</code> validator to any controls marked with the\n<code>required</code> attribute. The directive is provided with the <code><a href=\"api/forms/NG_VALIDATORS\" class=\"code-anchor\">NG_VALIDATORS</a></code> multi-provider list.</p>\n\n\n    \n  </section>\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n  \n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"see-also\">\n  <h2 id=\"see-also\">参见<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/RequiredValidator#see-also\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n  \n    <li><p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/form-validation\">表单验证</a></p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/form-validation\">Form Validation</a></p>\n\n</li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n\n\n  \n\n<h2 id=\"exported-from\">Exported from<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/RequiredValidator#exported-from\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<ul>\n\n  <li>\n    \n    <a href=\"api/forms/FormsModule\">\n      <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box\">FormsModule</code-example>\n    </a>\n    \n  </li>\n\n  <li>\n    \n    <a href=\"api/forms/ReactiveFormsModule\">\n      <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box\">ReactiveFormsModule</code-example>\n    </a>\n    \n  </li>\n\n</ul>\n\n\n  \n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"selector-list\">\n  <h2 id=\"selectors\">选择器<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/RequiredValidator#selectors\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  \n  <ul>\n    <li><code><i>:not([type=checkbox])</i>[required][<a href=\"api/forms/FormControlName\" class=\"code-anchor\">formControlName</a>]</code></li>\n    \n    <li><code><i>:not([type=checkbox])</i>[required][formControl]</code></li>\n    \n    <li><code><i>:not([type=checkbox])</i>[required][<a href=\"api/forms/NgModel\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngModel</a>]</code></li>\n    \n  </ul>\n  \n</section>\n\n\n\n  \n\n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"instance-properties\">\n  <a name=\"properties\"></a>\n  <h2 id=\"instance-properties\">属性<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/RequiredValidator#instance-properties\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table property-table\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr>\n        <th>属性</th>\n        <th>说明</th>\n      </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n    \n      <tr class=\"instance-property\">\n        <td>\n          <a id=\"required\"></a>\n          <code class=\"\"><span class=\"property-binding\">@<a href=\"api/core/Input\" class=\"code-anchor\">Input</a>()</span><br><span class=\"member-name\">required</span>: boolean | string</code>\n        </td>\n        <td>\n          \n          <div no-translate=\"\"><p translation-result=\"on\">跟踪对该指令绑定的 required 属性的更改。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Tracks changes to the required attribute bound to this directive.</p>\n\n</div>\n          \n          </td>\n    </tr>\n    \n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</section>\n\n\n\n  \n\n\n  \n  <section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"description\">\n    <h2 id=\"description\">说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/RequiredValidator#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    \n    <h3 id=\"adding-a-required-validator-using-template-driven-forms\" translation-result=\"on\">使用模板驱动表单添加必填项验证器<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/RequiredValidator#adding-a-required-validator-using-template-driven-forms\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3><h3 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"adding-a-required-validator-using-template-driven-forms\">Adding a required validator using template-driven forms<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/forms/RequiredValidator#adding-a-required-validator-using-template-driven-forms\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n\n<code-example>\n&lt;input name=\"fullName\" <a href=\"api/forms/NgModel\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngModel</a> required&gt;\n</code-example>\n\n  </section>\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n  \n  \n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/forms\n - api/forms/CheckboxRequiredValidator\n - api/forms/FormsModule\n - api/forms/ReactiveFormsModule\n - api/forms/Validator\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core/Input\n - api/forms\n - api/forms/FormControlName\n - api/forms/FormsModule\n - api/forms/NG_VALIDATORS\n - api/forms/NgModel\n - api/forms/ReactiveFormsModule\n - api/forms/RequiredValidator#adding-a-required-validator-using-template-driven-forms\n - api/forms/RequiredValidator#description\n - api/forms/RequiredValidator#exported-from\n - api/forms/RequiredValidator#instance-properties\n - api/forms/RequiredValidator#requiredvalidator\n - api/forms/RequiredValidator#see-also\n - api/forms/RequiredValidator#selectors\n - guide/form-validation\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/forms/src/directives/validators.ts?message=docs(forms)%3A%20请简述你的修改...#L349-L425\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/12.1.0-next.1/packages/forms/src/directives/validators.ts#L349-L425\n-->"}